# .cursorignore
# Best-effort exclusion from AI features (Tab, Chat, indexing, @-mentions).
# NOT a hard security boundary. Pair with Privacy Mode for regulated code.
# Terminal commands and MCP tools run outside these controls.

# --- Environment and local config ---
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
!.env.template

# --- Credentials and secrets ---
**/credentials*
**/secrets*
**/*secret*
**/*token*
**/*password*
**/service-account*.json
**/client_secret*.json

# --- Private keys and certificates ---
*.pem
*.key
*.p12
*.pfx
*.jks
*.keystore
**/.ssh/
**/id_rsa*
**/id_ed25519*

# --- Cloud provider credentials ---
**/.aws/credentials
**/.aws/config
**/.gcloud/
**/.azure/
**/.config/gcloud/

# --- Logs (may contain sensitive data) ---
*.log
**/logs/

# --- Runtime data ---
cache/*
input/*
output_md/*
output_txt/*
output_images/*
